title: WR & TE Rookie Preview + Best Landing Spots - Fantasy Football Podcast for 4/7
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, our rookie preview continues with wide receivers and tight ends! Which players should fantasy football players keep an eye out for during the NFL Draft? Plus, a game of “Who Am I?” and NFL News! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for April 7th, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(03:50) - Who Am I?
(08:45) - Stefon Diggs contract extension
(14:50) - Rookie Wide Receivers 
(17:05) - Garrett Wilson
(23:40) - Treylon Burks
(28:35) - Drake London
(33:50) - Chris Olave
(36:50) - Jameson Williams
(42:35) - Other Rookie WRs (Skyy Moore, Jahan Dotson, Christian Watson, George Pickens)
(47:20) - Rookie TEs (Trey McBride, Greg Dulcich)
